terms.term: A mental state where there is the least amount of noise in your brain thereby allowing you to feel focused, in the zone, and use 80% of your brain power.
An app that houses your customized neurohacks, that specifically work for you, to get your brain to green so you can perform your best.
A description of your current mental state, which may be described as green, yellow, or red.
An action you can take in 60 seconds or less to control the traffic signal in your brain and improve your mental temperature. There are physical, mental, and visual neurohacks.
A mental state where there is the most amount of noise in the brain, most distracted from task at hand, using only 5% of your brain power.

A mental state where there is average amount of noise in the brain, normally distracted from task at hand, using only 40% of your brain power. This is the state most of us function in on a daily basis.
